---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="CrazyQuizzes privacy policy — how we handle your data.">
  <div class="page-badge">★ LEGAL STUFF</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">PRIVACY<br><span style="color:#3bffd2;">POLICY</span></h1>
  <div class="page-body">
    <p><em>Last updated: June 2026</em></p>
    <p>CrazyQuizzes ("we", "us", "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and what rights you have.</p>

    <h2>WHAT WE COLLECT</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Quiz activity:</strong> We do not store your quiz answers or results on our servers. All quiz logic runs in your browser.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> We may collect anonymous analytics data (page views, session length, general location by country) to understand how the site is used. This data is not linked to you personally.</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use minimal cookies for basic site functionality. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>HOW WE USE YOUR DATA</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To operate and improve the site</li>
      <li>To understand which quizzes are popular</li>
      <li>To fix bugs and technical issues</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not sell your data. We do not share it with advertisers. We don't have a marketing list.</p>

    <h2>THIRD-PARTY SERVICES</h2>
    <p>We use Google Fonts to serve typefaces. Google may collect data as described in their own <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
    <p>Our site is hosted on Cloudflare. Cloudflare may process your IP address as part of their network infrastructure. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <h2>YOUR RIGHTS</h2>
    <p>Since we don't collect personal data, there's nothing to access, delete, or correct. If you have questions, email us at <a href="mailto:hello@crazyquizzes.com">hello@crazyquizzes.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>CHILDREN</h2>
    <p>CrazyQuizzes is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

    <h2>CHANGES TO THIS POLICY</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the site means you accept the updated policy.</p>

    <h2>CONTACT</h2>
    <p>Questions? <a href="/contact">Contact us.</a></p>
  </div>
</Layout>
